[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop music ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi! My name is Bea, and I'm a human interface designer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Documentation team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to share how to improve the discoverability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your Swift-DocC content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this session, I'll talk about the new navigation experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "available for Swift-DocC documentation on the web ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "and share tips for how to optimize your content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=27"
  },
  {
    "text": "for discoverability. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=29"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you need some additional context on what Swift-DocC is ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how you can make great documentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your frameworks and apps with it, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "check out these other WWDC sessions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=40"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's jump in and check out the new navigation on the web. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=44"
  },
  {
    "text": "This year, when you publish your documentation site, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "you get a new navigation experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "that brings out the best in your content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "The page contains two main sections. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "To the left is a navigator and filter bar that allow you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "to navigate through your documentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "and find APIs quickly. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=65"
  },
  {
    "text": "To the right is the content view. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's optimized to be flexible in multiple screen ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "and navigator sizes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since the navigator is separate from the content, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's easy to quickly switch between different pages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also use the disclosure indicators ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "to explore deeper in the tree ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "and understand the API hierarchy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "All of these features make it way easier ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "to explore documentation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "On the other hand, if you know what you're looking for ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "and you want to get there as quickly as possible, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can use the Filter bar to refine the results ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the navigator. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see the filter in action. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's say that you're looking for \"Habitat.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you click on the Filter bar and type that in, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll get a filtered view of the pages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "you actually care about, right now. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can clear the filter to reset the navigator. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "And you can also filter to see articles, tutorials, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "and even hide deprecated pages by selecting tags. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, if you select the Tutorials tag, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's super convenient to find ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "the \"Meet SlothCreator\" tutorial. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now that you're up to date with what's new in navigation, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=137"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to talk about how to make the most ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=141"
  },
  {
    "text": "out of this new experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=143"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here are some tips and tricks for how you can optimize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "your content so developers find the pages ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "they're looking for as smoothly as possible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me show you how I optimized the documentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "for my framework, SlothCreator, as an example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can use SlothCreator to catalog sloths ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "you find in nature and to create new, adorable virtual sloths. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "I just finished working on my framework documentation, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=169"
  },
  {
    "text": "so I haven't written any markdown ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "to organize my pages yet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=174"
  },
  {
    "text": "As a starting point, I'm taking advantage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "of Swift-DocC's automatic organization. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means my navigator is organized by types, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=182"
  },
  {
    "text": "like tutorials, articles, protocols, and structures. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is already a great start, but I can do a better job ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "guiding developers through my documentation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "To optimize my content, I'm going to follow three steps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=199"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, define the main high-level themes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "of what I can do with this framework. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=208"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, I'll organize my pages by importance and specificity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=210"
  },
  {
    "text": "Last but not least, I'll optimize my group titles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make sure they're as clear and helpful as possible. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "I think of this process as creating a map. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "It helps people understand the boundaries ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "and general characteristics of a region ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "and figure out how to get from one place to another. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=233"
  },
  {
    "text": "Likewise, the documentation navigator helps developers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "understand what you can do with a set of APIs ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how to navigate to the pages they're looking for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll start by helping developers understand what they can do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "with my APIs by defining the main high-level themes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=249"
  },
  {
    "text": "of SlothCreator. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=252"
  },
  {
    "text": "These themes will show up on the navigator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the SlothCreator page, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "the top-level page of my documentation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "It'll be one of the first things developers see ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "when they land on my documentation website. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is my opportunity to make a great first impression ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=267"
  },
  {
    "text": "and help developers have a good understanding ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "of what this framework does. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let me think about my first theme. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "One of the main functionalities of SlothCreator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=279"
  },
  {
    "text": "is creating sloths. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=281"
  },
  {
    "text": "They have names, colors, and even special powers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "To summarize, I'll call this topic group \"Sloth Creation\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "Later, I'll decide what pages to include in this group, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "so I'll just leave a placeholder for now. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "After you create a sloth, you can visualize it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=298"
  },
  {
    "text": "in many different ways, like on an app screen, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "in a map view. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll call this \"Sloth Views\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "And of course, sloths are a lot of work. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "They need to be fed, entertained, taken care of. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll call this \"Management\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's already a lot of functionalities ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can achieve in these three groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=323"
  },
  {
    "text": "And putting myself in the shoes of a developer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "who's never used SlothCreator before, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd love to have an easy way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "to see how to get started with this framework. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "With this in mind, I'll create a topic group ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "with high-level introductory content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll call it \"Essentials.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "Awesome! Even though there are hundreds of things ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can do with SlothCreator, I'm only highlighting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "the four most important, overarching topic groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "By reducing the number of options that are available, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=355"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm increasing developers' chances ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=358"
  },
  {
    "text": "of successfully taking the next step. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's no magic number for how many topic groups ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "I should create, but I generally try ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "to stick to under 10 per page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=369"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thinking back to the idea of a map, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to give developers step-by-step guidance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "on where they can go next. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "The order of my groups is vital to create a great experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "Taking another look at my topic groups, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=384"
  },
  {
    "text": "they're mostly in a good order. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, you have to create a sloth, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "then you can visualize it, then you can manage it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=391"
  },
  {
    "text": "The only thing I'd change here for now ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "is moving Essentials up to the beginning of the list, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "so developers see that beginner content first. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, it's time to decide the pages and themes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "that should be organized under each one of these categories. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me start with Essentials. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "This will be at the very top of the navigator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "and probably one of the first things developers will see. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=415"
  },
  {
    "text": "So I want to make sure this features ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "the most important introductory content. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=421"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a great spot to highlight ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "introductory articles and tutorials. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=427"
  },
  {
    "text": "This enables developers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "to find step-by-step code examples quickly, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is, personally, my favorite way to learn. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "With these considerations in mind, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "I decided to organize three groups under Essentials: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": "the \"Meet SlothCreator\" tutorial, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "the \"Getting Started with Sloths\" article, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=447"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the Sloth struct, one of the core APIs in my framework. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll repeat this same process for the three other groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=454"
  },
  {
    "text": "This feels approachable because I see the most important ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "and broad themes first. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "As I explore deeper in the tree, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "the groups get more specific and advanced. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "For instance, inside Essentials, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=469"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll find Getting Visual Attributes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=471"
  },
  {
    "text": "And inside Getting Visual Attributes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll find Getting the Standard Colors. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=475"
  },
  {
    "text": "Great, my documentation is organized in a way ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "to guide developers through the content successfully. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=482"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, I want to make sure the titles of my topic groups ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "are also high quality. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "The first characteristic to a great topic group title ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "is that it should be clear and descriptive. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=494"
  },
  {
    "text": "A good title makes sense on its own ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=498"
  },
  {
    "text": "and doesn't need much additional context. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thinking back to my topic titles, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=504"
  },
  {
    "text": "there's some room for improvement. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=506"
  },
  {
    "text": "The last topic title I wrote is \"Management.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "This group of APIs is all about what you can do ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=512"
  },
  {
    "text": "to manage your sloth's well-being: Activity, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "CareSchedule, FoodGenerator, and Sloth.Food. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "At first glance, this seems like a good title. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, upon further consideration, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Management\" is such a broad term; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=529"
  },
  {
    "text": "it could mean a ton of different things. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "So it's not ideal. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=534"
  },
  {
    "text": "To make this clearer and more descriptive, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=536"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to call it \"Care and Feeding.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I understand this group is all about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "taking care of my sloths and giving them food. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=544"
  },
  {
    "text": "For that reason, it's also important ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "that topic group titles be mutually exclusive. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=550"
  },
  {
    "text": "If I have titles that are interchangeable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's hard to know which one contains what I'm looking for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, Fueling Superpowers, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "Getting Magical Abilities, and Casting Enchantments ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "are very similar themes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "and could probably be organized under a single title. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "By keeping the names as mutually exclusive as possible, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=572"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm making it simpler for developers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=576"
  },
  {
    "text": "to figure out where to go next. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "The more work I put into organization and page titles, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=580"
  },
  {
    "text": "the more likely developers will have a smooth path ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the page they're looking for. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, the more likely I'll encourage serendipity; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "in other words, happy accidents. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "By organizing well-thought-out themes next to each other, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=596"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm enabling developers to find relevant, related pages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, as I'm learning about SlothCreator Essentials, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=605"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm delighted to find Getting Magical Abilities in the list. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=608"
  },
  {
    "text": "All of these tips and tricks ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "really brought my documentation to the next level. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=615"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so much better! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=618"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's review how you can improve the discoverability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your content and make it approachable for developers. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, identify the main themes of your documentation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, organize your content by importance and specificity. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, encourage serendipity, by organizing related themes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=639"
  },
  {
    "text": "next to each other. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=643"
  },
  {
    "text": "Last but not least, write clear, mutually exclusive titles ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your pages and groups. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you for taking the time ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "to learn how to make your documentation better. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=653"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm sure developers will deeply appreciate it. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "Have a great WWDC! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=660"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022-110369/?time=661"
  }
]